Deletes a node in the trie with a given key.

Parameters:
haystack The trie in which to search and destroy
key A null-terminated string identifying a node to destroy
Returns:
Returns 1 if the node indicated by key was found and destroyed.

Inserts a key / payload pair into the trie.

Parameters:
haystack The trie into which to insert the payload
key A null-terminated string to identify the payload.
payload The payload associated with this key.
flags Flags to control the behavior of the function when duplicate keys are found. See trie_insert_flags.
Returns:
